During this unprecedented time of conglomerate explosions of knowledge and information, Philippines has become the cornerstone of development, socio-economic progress, and even security, materializing our dreams and visions. The Department of Science and Technology (DOST) in cahoots with the Department of Public Works and Highways (DPWH), spearheaded the nationwide rollout of Information, Communications and Technology (ICT) Program lined up for both national government agencies and LGUs. The goal was to maximize efficiency and minimize wait time, which would help every sector run smoothly.

PCC has inadvertently reached and served hundreds of thousands of individuals and companies, ranging from normal citizens and progressive individuals, to medium to small scale enterprises and even government agencies. Among those who take advantage of our services are the following:
